  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC436">
        <l>ummai yecca miruvīṟ ṟāṉun</l>
	<l>taṉviṉai yoṉṟiya muṭipā kummē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/241/mode/1up">241</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/242/mode/1up">242</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, itu muṟaiyāṉē ummaiyeccattiṟku muṭipu kūṟutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : ummai yeccam eṉpatu eccavummaiyāyiṟṟu ; 'iruvīṟṟāṉum' eṉṟatu, tāṉum taṉṉāṟ ṟaḻuvappaṭṭatumāṉa iraṇṭaṉaiyum āyiṟṟu ; avai yiraṇṭum oṉṟiya viṉaiyē koṇṭumuṭiyum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu: 'cāttaṉumvantāṉ' eṉṟakkāl, piṉṉaik koṟṟaṉum vantāṉ eṉṟāṉum, koṟṟaṉum varum eṉpatāṉum oṉṟiyaviṉaiyēkoṇṭu muṭika eṉpatu ; 'cāttaṉum vantāṉ' eṉṟakkāl, 'koṟṟaṉum pōyiṉāṉ' eṉṟuviṭiṉ amaiyātu eṉpatām.	(40)</p>
    </body>
  </text>

